the 36th chamber of shaolin , also known as the master killer and shaolin master killer and shao lin san shi liu fang is a 1978 shaw brothers kung fu film directed by liu &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and starring gordon liu . the film follows a highly fictionalized version of san te , a legendary shaolin martial arts disciple who trained under the general chi shan . the 36th chamber of shaolin is widely considered to be one of the greatest kung fu films and a turning point in its director 's and star 's careers . it was followed by return to the 36th chamber , which was more comedic in presentation and featured gordon liu as the new main character with another actor in the smaller role of san te , and disciples of the 36th chamber .